<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Paymethod Update Form</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/reset.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/paymethod-update-form.css" />
</head>
<body>
<header>
    <div class="header-logo">
        <img src="/static/images/OH!FLIX.png" alt="Netflix Logo" />
    </div>
    <div class="logout">
        <a href="#">로그아웃</a>
    </div>
</header>
<!-- ---------------------------------------- -->
<div class="main">
    <div class="update-form-container">
        <a href="#" class="back-link">
            <img src="/static/images/system/arrow-left.svg" />결제 수단 변경</a
        >
        <h1>카드를 업데이트하세요</h1>
        <div class="icons">
            <img src="/static/images/cards/BC.png" alt="BC" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/Hana.png" alt="Hana" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/Hyundai.png" alt="Hyundai" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/KB.png" alt="KB" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/Lotte.png" alt="Lotte" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/NH.png" alt="NH" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/Samsung.png" alt="Samsung" />
            <img src="/static/images/cards/Shinhan.png" alt="Shinhan" />
            <!-- Add more icons as needed -->
        </div>
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <label for="card-number">카드 번호</label>
                    <div class="icon">
                        <img src="/static/images/system/card.svg" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <input type="text" id="card-number" class="card-input" required value="{{DetailDTO.cardNumber}}"/>
                <input type="hidden" id="cardNumberHidden" name="cardNumberHidden" />
            </div>


            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="expiry-date">유효기간</label>
                <input type="text" id="expiry-date" placeholder="MM/YY" value="{{DetailDTO.expiryMonth}}" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">이름</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" placeholder="이름" value="{{DetailDTO.cardOwner}}" />
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="dob">생년월일</label>
                <input type="date" id="dob" placeholder="생년월일" value="{{DetailDTO.dateOfBirth}}"/>
            </div>

            <div class="checkbox-container">
                {{^ DetailDTO.isAgreedThird}}
                    <input type="checkbox" id="agreement" />
                {{/DetailDTO.isAgreedThird}}
                {{# DetailDTO.isAgreedThird}}
                    <input type="checkbox" id="agreement" checked />
                {{/DetailDTO.isAgreedThird}}
                <span for="agreement"
                >본인의 개인 정보를 결제 서비스 업체에 제공하는 데에
              동의합니다.</span
                >
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="submit-button">저장</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- -------------------------------------------- -->
